query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ajax',
'android-listview',
'asp.net',
'azure-devops',
'google-drive-api',
'pivot',
'processing',
'sql-server-2008-r2',
'substring',
'swift4',
'swing',
'wordpress',
'xampp');
